name: Republic Airways E-190 [N177HQ] Landing in Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
This was a pleasant surprise to the spotters waiting for Air Canada's 777 inaugural flight from Frankfurt. I saw it coming on FlightRadar24, and the picture shown had it in the Frontier livery, so I was kind of disappointed when I found out it wasn't :( But any E-190 that's not Air Canada is definitely worth filming, lol. I hope you enjoy!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
